                        "content": "A clinic nurse prepares a teaching plan for a client receiving an antineoplastic medication. When implementing the plan, the nurse would make which statement to the client?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nBecause antineoplastic medications lower the resistance of the body, clients must be informed not to receive immunizations without the PHCP's approval. Clients also need to avoid contact with individuals who have recently received a live virus vaccine. Clients need to avoid aspirin and aspirin-containing products to minimize the risk of bleeding, and they need to avoid alcohol to minimize the risk of toxicity and side/adverse effects.",
                        "id": "7f98e5b5eb154725b758227faa14f4ef",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "3fb841d04b7f478f8fd5d25ab2e37f23",
                                "content": "Cyanosis"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "bd198a8445914faaa630d567d62664ab",
                                "content": "Arm edema"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "a30e1b8d85524d4796f0ec3e307015ad",
                                "content": "Periorbital edema"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "9bcd4be3fbe24b4b882d7b1eb339f50e",
                                "content": "Mental status changes"
                            }
                        ],
